---
// Minimal About Section
---

<section id="about" class="section-padding bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mb-16 fade-in-up">
      <p class="minimal-subheading mb-4">Who I Am</p>
      <h2 class="minimal-heading mb-6">About Me</h2>
      <p class="minimal-body">
        A UI/UX designer focused on creating clear, accessible, and measurable experiences through collaborative work with business and development teams.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Left: Story -->
      <div class="space-y-6 fade-in-up delay-100">
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          I transform user insights into effective interfaces by combining research, strategic thinking, and refined visual design. My approach focuses on understanding real problems before jumping into solutions.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          With experience in both design and development, I bridge the gap between creative vision and technical implementation, ensuring designs that are not only beautiful but also feasible and maintainable.
        </p>
        <hr class="minimal-divider">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <p class="minimal-subheading mb-2">Current Focus</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Research → Prototyping → Testing</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="minimal-subheading mb-2">Location</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Madrid, Spain</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="minimal-subheading mb-2">Availability</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Open for freelance projects & hybrid work</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Info cards -->
      <div class="space-y-6 fade-in-up delay-200">
        <div class="minimal-card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Specialties</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="minimal-tag">Accessibility</span>
            <span class="minimal-tag">Design Systems</span>
            <span class="minimal-tag">Prototyping</span>
            <span class="minimal-tag">UX Research</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="minimal-card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Design Tools</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Figma, FigJam, Notion, Framer</p>
        </div>

        <div class="minimal-card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Development</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">iOS (Swift), Angular, React, Astro</p>
        </div>

        <div class="minimal-card">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Approach</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">User-centered, data-driven, and collaborative. I believe the best designs emerge from close teamwork and continuous iteration.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
